Usage:

   1. Download the current version using the download link below, or here
   2. Open package:
          $ tar xzf filename.tar.gz 
   3. From the package directory, run autoconf script:
          $ ./configure
   4. Compile executable:
          $ make
   5. Run sample model:
          $ src/ds_bngl models/egfr_simple.bngl



NOTE:
 If running under CygWin (and possibly some other UNIX distributions),
 you may see an error about not being able to run "ps -o".  This
 error can safely be ignored.

